snippet.title: The Mighty Quest for Epic Loot - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The Mighty Quest for Epic Loot is a brand new Free-to-Play IP from Ubisoft Montreal for the PC that thrusts you in an outrageous medieval fantasy world called Opulencia where wealth, status and showboating are the name of the game!

Register now at: http://www.themightyquest.com


Want more news about The Mighty Quest for Epic Loot?

Like our Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/TheMightyQuestForEpicLoot?ref=hl
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/MightyQuest
And marvel at the awesomeness of our community's fan arts on Tumblr: http://themightyquest.tumblr.com/
